{"tid":39174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"秒回post","createTime":"2016-12-14T11:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:56:40.000Z","uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa52926fc3ceb8548f812f28d10b88bd2534382","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"11月分咗手<br />\n近排chur咗佢一星期多<br />\n唔想再chur 係佢樓下等緊佢講最後想法<br />\n有排等 有冇人想吹水"},{"pid":"f2ba61e8ab13a39d11f1d754d3b70fa94a7dde92","tid":39174,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"叫我？"},{"pid":"765c73fdcf61f54e04d5107b102645234feb2d76","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫我？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你 走啦你 我唔要分手啊"},{"pid":"eee8127640a12c83ebbab2415913517124571b0e","tid":39174,"uid":51398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"咩事分手？"},{"pid":"8d3cd035e00baf0fe8d4d90e2649f96011366acf","tid":39174,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"gi"},{"pid":"a5922a833102ddefdfd22b97e0c3a3baba26ed0d","tid":39174,"uid":2548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"好心人地唔再鍾意你就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08d74fb19a0ca06a0a2c00ba4b3421f6edffd0b","tid":39174,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫我？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你 走啦你 我唔要分手啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想嫁 人地唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6644f7016aaa27c4d027a13cbd84ec5d1506177f","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事分手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感受唔到佢嘅關心同重視<br />\n最後我忍唔到分手一個星期多 之後一齊返<br />\n佢一直都chur我一直返<br />\n但我冇 佢話我好絕 佢喊咗一個星期之後 覺得好攰唔想再拍<br />\n<br />\n過咗半個月多後 佢同我講返分手<br />\n話心淡咗好多 同埋我本身呷醋好勁 佢唔想再一齊<br />\n亦都唔想再痛"},{"pid":"255b142eb76cb7948e16809355a9893131e140db","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>gi</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849e1ce73d008327d6ab46a213121ac7bb36b7d0","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心人地唔再鍾意你就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過埋今次咪收皮<br />\n佢分手嗰日同我講 遲早都覺得會一齊返 但唔係而咖<br />\n話等佢考完試 睇下到時大家仲想唔想一齊"},{"pid":"01f2b0d2a6986cd3fd204ca913c61a540942a0c9","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫我？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你 走啦你 我唔要分手啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想嫁 人地唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n努力緊啊我"},{"pid":"a50fbcba231821720f5c68ab4fb200b275dff7f6","tid":39174,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"女人係咁仆街<br />\n不如考慮下同男人拍"},{"pid":"12bfde01d61abea723200fb329de91325d81ed55","tid":39174,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人係咁仆街<br />\n不如考慮下同男人拍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHehe?不了<br />\n係我一開始忍唔到 冇講問題出黎 果斷分咗手"},{"pid"